thread.title: Helen
thread.title_full: My Passport Photos reviewed by Helen

author: Helen
title: Helen
text: Working with My Passport Photos was easy and quick. I'm not a computer expert but was able to complete the application & download my photo with no problem. They quickly got back to me via email to let me know my order had been received and then contacted me a second time to request a different photo as the one I'd submitted was not complient for a US passport. After I submitted a new photo I received another email, "Great photo!" Nice that they took the time to let me know. Definitely a great way to get passport photos done.
